  ECHO PLAYER specialized variant of the 'normal' archnum listed below you can switch.
  ECHO PLAYER ------------------------------------------------------------------------
  ECHO PLAYER                 Normal    Light                        Normal    Light 
  ECHO PLAYER Weapon          Archnum   Archnum      Weapon          Archnum   Archnum 
  ECHO PLAYER ------------------------------------------------------------------------
