  ECHO PLAYER Bo-stick             5       993       Broadsword        1475      1252
  ECHO PLAYER Club                 9       700       Cutlass            290      1253
  ECHO PLAYER Dagger              12       885       Dirk                14      1098
  ECHO PLAYER Epee               499      1099       Flail             1537       801 
  ECHO PLAYER Foil               498      1188       Hammer             766       804
  ECHO PLAYER Katana              22      1070       Kusari-gama         23      1072
  ECHO PLAYER Longsword         1474      1254       Mace                25       955
  ECHO PLAYER Morning-star        42       956       Nunchaku            28      1220
  ECHO PLAYER Papenheimer        501       842       Pick               964       990
  ECHO PLAYER Poniard            503      1190       Rapier              32      1191
  ECHO PLAYER Sabre               34      1255       Sai                 35      1074
  ECHO PLAYER Scimitar            36      1256       Wakizashi           48      1089
  ECHO PLAYER Warhammer           49       992
  ECHO PLAYER ------------------------------------------------------------------------
ENDIF
