CALL 33
;
;
; Rake Mansion Rooms
;
; Variable List 3
VARIABLE RAKEKILL
;
NUMBER 3607
NAME Wine Cellar
*DESCRIPTION_START
You have entered the mansion's wine cellars, row upon row of carefully labeled
bottles, a testimony to the decadence of the mansion's inhabitants. Softly 
glowing lanters provide a subtle illumination. A rough stack of wooden crates
lies haphazardly against the far wall. Geoffrey, an ancient man in a faded 
tuxedo, stands here, keeping watch over the wines. A stairway leads back up
to the main sections of the mansion.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
;Old Wooden Wine Rack
ITEM 0 539 ADJ1=222 ADJ2=355 ADJ3=351
;Wooden Crate
ITEM 1 828  ADJ1=355
;Wall
ITEM 2 420
;Stairway
ITEM 7 81  VAL2=3606
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The old wooden racks are full of darkened bottles of wine.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFENTRY
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
    IFVAR ORG = 8
      ECHO ALL Geoffrey says, "Good day %N. How good it is to see you again."
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ORG ! 8
      IFCARRY 1893 427
        IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
          ECHO ALL Geoffrey says, "Good day %N. How good it is to see you again."
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ITEMBIT0 ! 1
          ECHO ALL Geoffrey stares coldly at %N and says, "May I help you?"
        ENDIF
      ELSE
        ECHO ALL Geoffrey stares coldly at %N and says, "May I help you?"
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB STOMP -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER The crate leads to room 323 [Hall of the Fellowship of Rakes]
    ECHO PLAYER Also, the sheathes to allow members in are ARCHNUM 1893, ADJ 427 ITEMBIT0 1
    ECHO PLAYER Lastly, SET RAKEKILL 1 to allow combat in this room.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    AFFECT 323
    ECHO ALL %P arrives through a concealed opening.
    AFFECT 3607
    MOVEGROUP 323
  ENDIF
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
    IFVAR ORG = 8
      ECHO PLAYER You feel around for the familiar opening, and enter the guild hall proper.
      ECHO OTHERS %N taps at the far wall, and vanishes amidst the crates.
      AFFECT 323
      ECHO ALL %N arrives through a concealed opening.
      AFFECT 3607
      MOVE 323
    ENDIF
    IFVAR ORG ! 8
      IFCARRY 1893 427
        IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
          ECHO PLAYER You feel around for the familiar opening, and enter the guild hall proper.
          ECHO OTHERS %N taps at the far wall, and vanishes amidst the crates.
          AFFECT 323
          ECHO ALL %N arrives through a concealed opening.
          MOVE 323
          AFFECT 3607
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ITEMBIT0 ! 1
          ECHO PLAYER You feel around amidst the crates as Geoffrey eyes you disapprovingly, but don't find anything.
          ECHO OTHERS %N fumbles around in the crates.
        ENDIF
      ELSE
        ECHO PLAYER You feel around amidst the crates as Geoffrey eyes you disapprovingly, but don't find anything.
        ECHO OTHERS %N fumbles around in the crates.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO OTHERS %N sniffs.
  ECHO PLAYER You smell the strong, pungent odor of ageing wine.
ENDIF
IFSAY ADMIT
  IFVAR ORG = 8
    IFVAR ORGRANK > 199
      ECHO PLAYER Geoffrey nods to you and signals below the others line of vision.
      ECHO ALL Several burly guards appear, and escort %N's party through an opening in the wall that wasn't there a moment ago.
      AFFECT 323
      ECHO ALL Several burly guards appear, leading %N's party into the hall.
      MOVEGROUP 323
      AFFECT 3607
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY WINE
  IFVAR ORG = 8
    IFITEM 3
      ECHO PLAYER Geoffrey says, "You'll have to take the glass that's there, first."
    ENDIF
    IFNOITEM 3
      ECHO PLAYER Geoffrey nods to you, placing a glass of wine before you.
      ECHO OTHERS Geoffrey fetches %N a glass of wine.
      NEWITEM 3 546
      NEWPUT 3 237  VAL3=5
    ENDIF
   ENDIF
    IFVAR ORG ! 8
      ECHO PLAYER Geoffrey raises an eyebrow towards you questioningly.
      ECHO OTHERS Geoffrey raises an eyebrow towards %N questioningly.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
IFVAR RAKEKILL ! 1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
    IFPREVERB KILL -1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO OTHERS Geoffrey frowns at %N, and snaps his fingers.
      ECHO OTHERS Two burly men appear, grab %N and haul %i up the stairs.
      ECHO PLAYER Geoffrey frowns at you, and snaps his fingers.
      ECHO PLAYER Two burly men appear, grab you by the arms, haul you up the stairs, and toss you into the street.
      POSITION SIT
      MOVE 273
      AFFECT 273
      ECHO OTHERS Two burly men appear on the front stairs of the mansion and hurl %N into the street.
      AFFECT 3607
    ENDIF
    IFPREVERB CAST -1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER Geoffrey shakes his head at you and says, "We'll have none of that in here."
    ENDIF
    IFPREVERB PROJECT -1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER Geoffrey shakes his head at you and says, "We'll have none of that in here."
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
CALL 33
;
NUMBER 323
NAME Hall of the Fellowship of Rakes
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room is the heart of the guild of Rakes. A huge round mohagany table fills the room, surrounded by twelve comfortable looking leather padded chairs. Each of the four walls of this room is painted with the symbol of one of the gods; Amilor to the north, Rorin to the south, Shemri to the east and Ordanin to the west. Set into each wall is a titanium door. The four doors lead to the offices of the four officials of the guild. There is also an arch, leading to the training area of the Rakes, from which you can hear many excited grunts and cries.
*DESCRIPTION_END
