*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
This is a large, dark wooden table, lacquered and stained. The seal of the Kentaurus family adorns each of the four corners. Various ring-shaped stains reveal where careless members have left their drinks. A large map of Fayd is set into the table's surface, beneath the glossy finish.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The large, detailed map depicts the entire city of Fayd. Certain areas are marked in red or white, and many small colored dots mark the entrances to various guilds, and secret locations.
*DESCRIPTION_END
