As you enter the room the first thing that catches your eye is a painting that
is mounted upon the wall behind the heavy oak desk. On the left side of the
room is a bookshelf that is filled with books dealing with martial arts forms
and history. On the right side of the room is a smaller desk that is scattered 
with scrolls, tomes and various writing implements.
*DESCRIPTION_END
