NUMBER 324
NAME Rake Hall, Training
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
In this room, some of the former finest swordsmen of Fayd, retired due to age
or injury, teach their trade to many eager young Rakes. Some students carefully
learn the heft and swing of a sword; others study anatomical diagrams, seeking
the vulnerable areas; others delve into more arcane mysteries. A plain wooden
door is the obvious exit, but there is also a small, dark opening, leading to
places unknown.
*DESCRIPTION_END
