NUMBER 18
NAME Foundry
FIXED_LIGHT
FORGE
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
In the midst of this open yard, only a tin lean-to shelters the forge from the weather. A murg laborer pumps huge bellows and feeds the fire from the stockpile of dry logs stacked around the yard's perimeter. There are also piles of steel, which is on sale here for five crowns. Near the back, a corrugated metal shed with a weatherbeaten door houses the Weaponsmiths' Union Hall. A black iron gate goes back to the street.
*DESCRIPTION_END
